          <h2><li>Key points of Ai.</li></h2>
        <article class="blog-post">
          <h3><a href="#">Here's a breakdown of the key points about AI:
             <li>Goal: To create machines capable of performing tasks that typically require human intelligence.</li>
            <li>Capabilities: AI systems can learn from data, identify patterns, make predictions, and respond to their environment.</li>
            <li>Types: There are different types of AI, ranging from basic reactive machines to those with more advanced capabilities like theory of mind.</li>
            <li>Applications: AI is used in various fields, including healthcare, finance, transportation, and entertainment.</li></a></h3>
